The paper deals with the problem of secret key establishment over broadcast channels, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the concept of secrecy potential, which is a common topic in cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed Interactive Channel Coding (ICC) technique is a form of coding, which falls under the category of coding theory (cs.CC).
